snippet.title: Echo Combat | New Dyson Map and New Gear
snippet.description:
Join the battle in zero-g!

Team up with friends, choose your gear, and secure the objective to achieve victory in Echo Combat, available November 15th. 

You can purchase Echo Combat for $9.99 via the Oculus Store, the Echo VR Main Menu, or at any of the Matchmaking/Customization Terminals in the Lobby




Follow us on social for regular Echo Unit updates:
Twitter: https://twitter.com/echogames
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/echogamesVR
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/echogamesvr/
Patch Notes: https://medium.com/echo-games-blog
